snippet.title: Amber Rose on Similarities with Trump & Kanye, Dating 21 Savage (Full Interview)
snippet.description:
In this full interview, Amber Rose discussed her previous relationships (e.g. Kanye West and 21 Savage).  Throughout the one-on-one. Amber Rose reveals her upbringing, womanhood, slut-shaming, and her past life as a dancer. To hear more, including where Amber says she got her values, hit the above clip.

Video credit: The Fallen State TV
